{"tid":1511270,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府提意緊急法 ，背後之意⋯","createTime":"2019-08-27T13:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T13:57:44.000Z","uid":187007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"794e679c23aaf38e09baf405288dfc4b4ec56cda","tid":1511270,"uid":187007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:13:18.000Z","msg":"都有一個可能性就係 停止哂海陸空出入境<br />\n<br />\n停哂上網 逼外國撒僑撒記者 <br />\n<br />\n邊個再上街就拉，有沖擊人數太多就<br />\n<br />\n深圳關口正式入境 重演30年前一幕？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以回想番當年官士講既對白 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左政權 放棄一小部份既人佢地係覺得值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>距離成功愈近我地反而要愈小心<br />\n而個位置先愈容易大意</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各大商家佬正常7月開始不斷對政府施壓，但政府到<br />\n<br />\n現在完全控制唔到情況，仲意圖立緊急法。<br />\n<br />\n逼虎跳牆，立緊急法可能都係通知有財有勢既撒⋯<br />\n<br />\n強如孔明既誠哥早幾年而暴走特急撒資成功<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，條例/示威/暴動/緊急法/ 一切都如劇本跟<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭一樣，幸好結局親俄總統亞努科維奇流亡<br />\n<br />\n但都要注意⚠️親俄 俄羅斯～中國關係 近日香港政<br />\n<br />\n府做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以下開放討論"},{"pid":"fb01f49cd31135aa382c0a0dff9575c7eabfd686","tid":1511270,"uid":245441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:14:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">未立法先撤資 阿爺d錢走唔到呀！</span>"},{"pid":"9bc4ad722fc6c1b657c69045172c6a47d2e9b58e","tid":1511270,"uid":184787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"794e679c23aaf38e09baf405288dfc4b4ec56cda","tid":1511270,"uid":187007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:13:18.000Z","msg":"都有一個可能性就係 停止哂海陸空出入境<br />\n<br />\n停哂上網 逼外國